contract_title: 2025 Master Services Agreement - AI Strategy Consulting

sections.details: Provide ongoing strategic consulting for the development and deployment of next-generation large language models and generative AI platforms.

Tiered pricing for consultation hours. The first 20 hours per month are billed at $400/hr. All subsequent hours in the same month are billed at a discounted rate of $325/hr. Invoices are to be submitted monthly, Net 30.
This agreement is governed by the laws of the State of Delaware. All work performed under this agreement is considered confidential and the intellectual property of Global Innovations Corp.
